description: Keep an eye out for a big and colorful umbrella around the downtown area, because that’s where you’ll find Melissa’s Pal Crépes. Chicago’s first ever mobile vendor is serving up a fantastically tasty array of sweet & savory crépes, fresh salads & fruit cups, pasta bowls, Hot Tamales, sandwiches, hot dogs, the mother-in-law, and that’s not even all. You can also order up some authentic and delicious Serbian cuisine (with meat and vegetarian options), all made with the freshest local ingredients. Whether you’re looking for your next meal, or for something really yummy to feed your guests at your next event, Melissa’s Pal Crépes is the perfect cart for you.
name: Melissa's Pal Crépes
